  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Le Val Chaviere is on a half board.</p>
<p>A buffet breakfast is available each morning between 8-10am with a range of sweet and savoury options,</p>
<p>Each evening you'll enjoy a set five course set evening meal is served each night including soup, starter, set main course, choice of cheeses and a dessert buffet. Plus each week there is a regional fondue and for those who do not like cheese, the fondue can be Bourguignonne style (meat dipped in oil). One choice of main, starters and dessert not included on the regional evening. </p>
<p><strong> Alternative meals for special dietary requirements is not available, meat is replaced by eggs or fish for pescatarians. </strong></p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners are included.</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
