  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>Le Val Chavieres 49 rooms overlook the surrounding mountains, south-west facing rooms look towards the 'pointe de la Masse' and the south-east facing rooms look over the 'les aiguilles de Peclet'.</p>
<p><strong>Twin Bedrooms</strong> sleep two people and are around 17m², with a balcony with mountain views. These rooms are also available for sole occupancy for a supplement.</p>
<p><strong>Twin Plus Bedrooms</strong> around 18m² sleeping two adults and a child, with a balcony with a mountain view.  </p>
<p><strong>Family rooms</strong> sleep two adults and two children and are around 20-25m². Family rooms have a double bed or twin beds, plus bunk beds suitable for children. This room type is available on request so please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Bath with shower head attachment or shower room</li>
<li>WC</li>
<li>Daily house keeping is included</li>
<li>Baby cots are available on request. Free for children under 2 years old. </li>
<li>Both room types can accommodate a cot</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
